1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,050
[Episode 39]

2
00:00:04,390 --> 00:00:07,510
What are you looking at?
Do I have something on my face?

3
00:00:11,270 --> 00:00:12,030
Yes.

4
00:00:15,430 --> 00:00:18,230
What is it? I don't see anything.

5
00:00:19,550 --> 00:00:24,790
It's... your cuteness.

6
00:00:26,870 --> 00:00:30,710
Ugh, what a cheesy line.

7
00:00:34,910 --> 00:00:36,270
Do you like it though?

8
00:00:40,430 --> 00:00:46,550
Bin, I want to ask you something.

9
00:00:51,750 --> 00:01:06,510
Well... is it possible that
um...

10
00:01:08,789 --> 00:01:11,830
Just say what's on your mind.

11
00:01:17,789 --> 00:01:20,110
Is it possible...

12
00:01:21,750 --> 00:01:23,470
That we...

13
00:01:27,230 --> 00:01:30,230
Could date seriously?

14
00:01:30,950 --> 00:01:35,830
Why? Because I'm handsome?

15
00:01:35,830 --> 00:01:46,310
No. When you're not around,
I miss you.

16
00:01:48,630 --> 00:01:54,789
But when you're with me,
I miss you even more.

17
00:01:55,870 --> 00:01:59,850
I keep asking myself,

18
00:02:02,190 --> 00:02:05,750
why you're always on my mind.

19
00:02:10,030 --> 00:02:22,230
I want to know what you're doing,
where you are, how you're doing.

20
00:02:25,350 --> 00:02:31,390
And that makes me want to know you better.

21
00:02:34,150 --> 00:02:39,070
Finally, I found the answer.

22
00:02:41,329 --> 00:02:46,870
You are the one
I truly want.

23
00:02:50,190 --> 00:02:52,079
Only you.

24
00:02:55,160 --> 00:03:03,910
In the past, I never dared to admit
I liked you.

25
00:03:06,150 --> 00:03:11,790
Because I messed things up before.

26
00:03:35,930 --> 00:03:38,610
[To Be Continued]
